data.description:
For the 2017 track1 baseline, we used 39 dimensions MFCC+Delta+Delta2 features computed every 10ms and the ABX score was computed using the frame-wise cosine distance averaged along the DTW path.
Baseline for the 2017 track2 is computed using the software from https://github.com/arenjansen/ZRTools.
